      "widgets_values": [
        "# MODELS AND NODES USED IN THIS WORKFLOW  \n\n---\n\n## 🟣 Load Diffusion Model\n### Download **z-image-turbo_fp8_scaled_e5m2_KJ.safetensors** ~6GB from [HERE](https://huggingface.co/Kijai/Z-Image_comfy_fp8_scaled/resolve/main/z-image-turbo_fp8_scaled_e5m2_KJ.safetensors?download=true)\n\n📁 **Place in:** `ComfyUI/models/diffusion_models/z-image` \n\nCreate the `z-image` folder if it does not exist)\n \nMore info about the FP8 models [HERE](https://huggingface.co/Kijai/Z-Image_comfy_fp8_scaled/tree/main)\n\n---\n\n## 🟣 Load CLIP\n\n###  Download **qwen_3_4b_fp8_mixed.safetensors* from [HERE](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/z_image_turbo/resolve/main/split_files/text_encoders/qwen_3_4b_fp8_mixed.safetensors)\n\n📁 **Place in:** `ComfyUI/models/text_encoders`  \n\n--- \n\n## 🟣 Load VAE\n\n### Download the **ae.safetensor** (flux 1 vae) from [HERE](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/z_image_turbo/resolve/main/split_files/vae/ae.safetensors)  \n\n📁 **Place in:** `ComfyUI/models/vae`  \n\n---\n\n## 🧩 Nodes Installed from Manager  \n\n- None\n\n---\n\n## 📚 Resources  \n🎥 **Tutorials:** [Pixaroma YouTube Channel](https://www.youtube.com/@pixaroma)  \n💬 **Community Discord:** [Join Here](https://discord.com/invite/gggpkVgBf3)\n"
