      "widgets_values": [
        "{\"version\":1,\"content\":\"<h1>MODELS AND NODES USED IN THIS WORKFLOW</h1><p>\\n\\n</p><hr class=\\\"pix-note-hr-solid\\\" style=\\\"color: #b8b8b8\\\"><p>\\n\\n</p><h2><span data-ic=\\\"model-v1\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\" style=\\\"color: #f66744\\\"></span>&nbsp;Load Diffusion Model</h2><p>\\n\\n<span class=\\\"pix-note-btnblock\\\">\\n  <a class=\\\"pix-note-dl\\\" style=\\\"background-color: #f66744\\\" href=\\\"https://huggingface.co/Kijai/Z-Image_comfy_fp8_scaled/resolve/main/z-image-turbo_fp8_scaled_e5m2_KJ.safetensors?download=true\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\">Download z-image-turbo_fp8_scaled_e5m2_KJ.safetensors<span class=\\\"pix-note-btnsize\\\">~6 GB</span></a>\\n</span>&nbsp;\\n\\n</p><div class=\\\"pix-note-folderhint\\\" style=\\\"color: #f66744\\\">Place in: ComfyUI/models/diffusion_models/z-image</div><p>\\n\\n</p><p>Create the <code>z-image</code> folder if it does not exist.</p><p>\\n\\n<span class=\\\"pix-note-btnblock\\\">\\n  <a class=\\\"pix-note-rm\\\" style=\\\"background-color: #f66744\\\" href=\\\"https://huggingface.co/Kijai/Z-Image_comfy_fp8_scaled/tree/main\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\">More info about FP8 models</a>\\n</span>&nbsp;\\n\\n</p><hr class=\\\"pix-note-hr-solid\\\" style=\\\"color: #b8b8b8\\\"><p>\\n\\n</p><h2><span data-ic=\\\"CLIP\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\" style=\\\"color: #f66744\\\"></span>&nbsp;Load CLIP</h2><p>\\n\\n<span class=\\\"pix-note-btnblock\\\">\\n  <a class=\\\"pix-note-dl\\\" style=\\\"background-color: #f66744\\\" href=\\\"https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/z_image_turbo/resolve/main/split_files/text_encoders/qwen_3_4b_fp8_mixed.safetensors\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\">Download qwen_3_4b_fp8_mixed.safetensors<span class=\\\"pix-note-btnsize\\\">~8 GB</span></a>\\n</span>&nbsp;\\n\\n</p><div class=\\\"pix-note-folderhint\\\" style=\\\"color: #f66744\\\">Place in: ComfyUI/models/text_encoders</div><p>\\n\\n</p><hr class=\\\"pix-note-hr-solid\\\" style=\\\"color: #b8b8b8\\\"><p>\\n\\n</p><h2><span data-ic=\\\"VAE\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\" style=\\\"color: #f66744\\\"></span>&nbsp;Load VAE</h2><p>\\n\\n<span class=\\\"pix-note-btnblock\\\">\\n  <a class=\\\"pix-note-dl\\\" style=\\\"background-color: #f66744\\\" href=\\\"https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/z_image_turbo/resolve/main/split_files/vae/ae.safetensors\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\">Download ae.safetensors<span class=\\\"pix-note-btnsize\\\">VAE</span></a>\\n</span>&nbsp;\\n\\n</p><div class=\\\"pix-note-folderhint\\\" style=\\\"color: #f66744\\\">Place in: ComfyUI/models/vae</div><p>\\n\\n</p><hr class=\\\"pix-note-hr-solid\\\" style=\\\"color: #b8b8b8\\\"><p>\\n\\n</p><p><span data-ic=\\\"warning-v1\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\" style=\\\"color: #f66744\\\"></span>&nbsp;After placing the files, restart ComfyUI or refresh model lists using the <b>R</b> shortcut.</p><p>\\n\\n</p><hr class=\\\"pix-note-hr-solid\\\" style=\\\"color: #b8b8b8\\\"><p>\\n\\n</p><h2><span data-ic=\\\"nodes-installed\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\" style=\\\"color: #f66744\\\"></span>&nbsp;Nodes Installed from Manager</h2><p>\\n\\n</p><ul>\\n  <li>Pixaroma</li>\\n</ul><p>\\n\\n</p><hr class=\\\"pix-note-hr-solid\\\" style=\\\"color: #b8b8b8\\\"><p>\\n\\n</p><h2><span data-ic=\\\"pixaroma\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\" style=\\\"color: #f66744\\\"></span>&nbsp;Resources</h2><p>\\n\\n</p><p>\\n  <a class=\\\"pix-note-discord\\\" href=\\\"https://discord.com/invite/gggpkVgBf3\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\">Join Discord</a>&nbsp;\\n\\n  <a class=\\\"pix-note-yt\\\" href=\\\"https://www.youtube.com/@pixaroma\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\">Pixaroma YouTube Channel</a>&nbsp;\\n</p>\",\"bu